[normal] 
[normal]Scotland’s
[normal] 
[normal]supply chain totalled
[normal] 
[normal]£17.2bn
[normal] 
[normal]in
[normal] 
[normal]2011,
[normal] growing 
[normal]by
[normal] 5.8 
[normal]per
[normal] c
[normal]ent
[normal] 
[normal]from
[normal] 
[normal]2010.
[normal] 
[normal]I
[normal]nternati
[normal]onal
[normal] sales 
[normal]increased
[normal] 
[normal]by
[normal] 8.4
[normal] 
[normal]per cent
[normal] 
