[normal] billion
[normal] in 2011, with North America remaining the 
[normal]main
[normal] export
[normal] market. Scotti
[normal]sh
[normal] exports to
[normal] Norway, 
[normal]Angola, Nigeria an
[normal]d the UAE are also strong
